      "review_summary": "The PR adds a helper that maps `.docodex`, `.pptcodex`, and `.xlscodex` to Office extensions and applies it to shared write/edit validation plus the read wrapper.\n\nPR surface: Source +59, Tests +135. Total +194 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main and v2026.6.8 leave a supplied `.docodex` path unchanged through XML-only normalization. I did not establish a deterministic live model turn that produces the hallucinated suffix.",
